* Desmonus watches Zardus carefully as he recieves a message over his 
com-link, then deactivating it and flying off in the direction of the 
battle.
She watched for a moment before silantly transforming into Beast Mode, 
hissing as she stretched her wings and then lifted her cobra body into the 
air.
This was the first time that she had actually flown but it seemed almost as 
if she had done so for years.
Desmonus followed Zardus towards the Battlefield.*
